		<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns">
			<strong>Drive-Through Team Member</strong>
			<p>
				While working at Tim Hortons, I was part of the drive-through team providing customers with fast quality service. I dealt with any customer concerns that was brought to my attention as professionally as possible. At Tim Hortons I developed strong communication skills as a result of taking drive-through orders.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

